LINE.Text: You know the BASIC TRAFFIC LAWS -
Stop at a red light, Obey the speed limit,
But this is America, land of the free and home of
the make-it-up-as-you-go-along, so in addition to
the standard traffic laws, there are some weird and
wacky ones out there that could blow your mind.
Pay ticket if you drive with a
gorilla in the back-seat of your car
illegal to shoot whales from car
No frowing at a police officer
No swearing on highway in Rockville
If you are drunk and not driving your car,
and the person who is driving the car is
drunk as well, you may both receive DUIs
Tourist states like Nevada, Hawaii, Alaska and
California enforce laws against driving too slow
Cars may not drive on the streets of Redlands, Calif.
unless a man with a lantern is walking ahead of it.
In Georgia, members of the state assembly cannot be
ticketed for speeding while assembly is in session.
It is illegal to molest a car in Clinton, Oklahoma
No drinking beer in country parking lot
